CLI squad sent out survey to understand which platforms users will be installing the Zowe CLI on. 
Results are below:

Questions: On what platform do you or would you like to run the Zowe CLI on?
*32 Responses* (Select all boxes that apply)

- Mac: 14 (40.6%)
- Linux: 15 (46.9%)
- Windows: 22 (68.8%)
- Other: z/OS - 2 (6.2%) 

Link to Survey: https://goo.gl/forms/Sfqo4Jd4qDiEWjD03
